paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the role of the C-terminal β9-strand in the cNBH domain of Kv11.1 channels and its impact on channel gating and trafficking. Two clinically relevant mutations in the KCNH2 gene are mentioned, but specific variant details are not provided.

challenges: The paper discusses mutations in the KCNH2 gene but does not provide specific variant details or penetrance data.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper focuses on the functional role of the β9-strand in Kv11.1 channels and mentions clinical mutations without specifying the exact variants or providing penetrance data.
